WEBVTT

00:00:04.220 --> 00:00:06.560
Pat Mitchell: It's so great
to see you, my friend.

00:00:06.584 --> 00:00:09.167
Jane Fonda: Hi Pat.
It's great to be with you.

00:00:09.191 --> 00:00:14.237
PM: Jane, for the ones who may not
have seen the extraordinary coverage

00:00:14.261 --> 00:00:15.959
around the world

00:00:15.983 --> 00:00:17.925
of Fire Drill Fridays

00:00:17.949 --> 00:00:22.204
and the impact that they have already had,

00:00:22.228 --> 00:00:25.744
talk to us about the origin of this idea,

00:00:25.768 --> 00:00:29.955
this particular response
to the climate crisis.